%F A028173 a(n) = (12^(n+3)-7*8^(n+3)+14*6^(n+3)-8*5^(n+3))/168. - _Yahia Kahloune_, Jun 03 2013
%F A028173 a(n) = 6^(n+1)-5^(n+1)+20*a(n-1)-96*a(n-2). - _Vincenzo Librandi_, Jul 15 2026
